### 0. 注册用户（如果登录失败，先执行此步骤）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "email": "test@campus.com",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 1. 先登录（获取 Session）
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser&password=123456

### 2. 创建订单（立即购买）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/create?articleId=1&quantity=1&address=武汉市洪山区

### 3. 获取我的订单（买家）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/my

### 4. 获取卖家订单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/seller

### 5. 获取订单详情（把 {id} 换成实际订单号）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### 6. 取消订单（把 {id} 换成实际订单号）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel?reason=不想要了

### 7. 确认收货（把 {id} 换成实际订单号）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/confirm

### 8. 卖家发货（把 {id} 换成实际订单号）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/ship

### 9. 评价订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "articleId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "content": "商品很好，非常满意！"
}